i'm trying to set variable in the key section of the labels when
creating google_compute_instance"

this is possible:

    labels {
        "billing-zone"          = "${var.zone}"
      }

but this:

    labels {
        "${var.zone}"          = ""
      }

is not. ( the var can be only in the value section )
is there anyway to pass that?

Thank you.

